Wait. We still need to include cash flow hits that don=E2=80=99t show up on=
 the P&L. A new outdoor sign cost $4k, and SBA loan principal payments cost=
 $17k, and, in Charlie=E2=80=99s words, =E2=80=9CJust like that our (barely=
) profitable restaurant ended the year with $8,000 less in cash than we sta=
rted with.=E2=80=9D
I put it all into a spreadsheet and included a running balance column for t=
he same reason I included so much detail in the last few paragraphs: so you=
