irect/c8b42c83-4b1d-4240-a238-3d5d04352987?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7Gn=
A_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ].
I=E2=80=99ll spare you the gory details, but on $1,215,037 in income from t=
he restaurant and catering business, Mei Mei ended 2019 with=E2=80=A6=C2=A0
That=E2=80=99s before, Li said, debt repayment and taxes. =E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=
=99s not nothing. It=E2=80=99s not great. But this is where we are.=E2=80=
=9D
Both of those examples are from 2019. Then COVID hit. Then food prices infl=
