ze: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">While memberships were re=
staurant-specific, $FLY would be a &#8220;pan-industry loyalty currency.&#8=
221; Every time you check in at Gertie, for example, you might receive 1,00=
