ion is building products that consumers love. It has nothing to do with cry=
pto, per se.&#8221;&#160;</strong></p></li></ol><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, =
55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">But, havi=
ng built traditional software products, Ben chose to bring crypto into the =
mix at Blackbird, despite the regulatory complexity and technical challenge=
