es, who is dedicated to helping the restaurant industry, and who wouldn&#82=
17;t have built on blockchain rails if it didn&#8217;t serve that goal.&#16=
0;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26p=
x; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">So why bring crypto into it?&#160;</p><p style=3D"c=
